Directors’ Remuneration

Manager Nominated Directors do not receive any fees for serving as a director or a member of a committee of the Board.

Directors (including the Manager Nominated Directors) are reimbursed for reasonable out-of—pocket expenses incurred in attending meetings of the Board or Board committees and for any expenses reasonably incurred in their capacity as directors of the Company or any of its subsidiaries.
